cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. The use of neural networks and deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves reinforcement learning, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of ROUGE as a metric suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
